245
00:17:12,154 --> 00:17:14,736
obedient, apathetic,

246
00:17:15,133 --> 00:17:17,947
separated, atomized individuals.

247
00:17:18,047 --> 00:17:24,103
The ideal social unit is a pair:
you and a television set.

